Details: Jamboree is the oldest institute in India and the best of its kind, which offers comprehensive classroom preparation programs for tests such as GMAT, GRE, SAT, TOEFLTM and IELTS. Jamboree centres are present in 14 cities of India and in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and Kathmandu . Each centre follows a uniform curriculum and has outstanding faculty, all of whom are trained in our head office. Each centre offers the same teaching standards and syllabus.At Jamboree, the most trusted name in India for education abroad, we help you give shape to your career and dreams. Founded in 1993, Jamboree attempted to fill the information gap on education abroad. Back then, the only information available on education abroad was through friends and family living or studying abroad. Thus, only a small percentage of interested students had access to information. Jamboree attempted to fill this information gap. Now when we in 'Team Jamboree' reflect on the past few years, we see thousands of our students on the thresholds of careers that would not have been possible without the right guidance at the right time.Jamboree, known for its thorough research and professionalism, is a one-stop shop for education abroad.Jamboree makes the entire process of studying abroad, from preparing to actually joining a foreign university, a smooth process. In recent years, the inclusion of several value-added services such as discounted couriers, educational loans and pre-departure orientation has made Jamboree Education Pvt. Ltd. a one-stop solution centre for all your study abroad requirements.

Details: Mascot Forum is a forum to catapult forum goals. High standards and quality education are its hallmarks. It aims to render its educational obligations commensurate with great expectations of students and the high standards of premier universities abroad. The Forum has outstanding faculty members who have wealth of experience in teaching and content writing. Their guidance and pedagogic skills have metamorphosed the Forum into an institution par excellence.By now the Forum has established perfect credentials as reliable institution to address and deliver various forum requirements of aspirants willing to study overseas. Our training facilities are tailored to suit their personal priorities and preferences. Other than running routine batches for general students at our centre and doing write ups etc, we also undertake personal classes online or at your doorstep.One of the major tasks foremost on our mind is straightening out the lack of sound basics in English and mathematics among certain students. While IELTS and TOEFL assess only English language skills, GMAT, GRE and SAT require good proficiency in both mathematics and English of rather a higher level to obtain a good score and get admission in a prestigious university. Those who have skills below the mark, lag behind though they could otherwise be intelligent students. To bridge this vacuum, our Forum runs specialist courses which act as go- between the above courses and improving on basics in mathematics and English. Not only this, those who are concerned about their being behind whilst studying in the school and wish to make up for their shortcomings by the time they graduate high school, the Academy lends special support to such students through private tuitions to improve their school results with emphasis on building overall competence in the two subjects. We believe that probably its the right step at the right time to take on future academic challenges.

Experienced and well qualified faculty and committed support staff are the hall mark of ASEL. ASEL has branches in Central Delhi(Connaught Place) and South Delhi. Our aim is to motivate and guide our students with the help of expert faculty to speak English fluently and confidently. Importance of Learning English Language cannot be denied. It is the most spoken official language in the world. Knowledge of the English Language can create many opportunities for all and in turn double the chances of earning more. Fluency in English is essential for professional and personal growth as well as success in all sectors. Excel in the language with right courses that we provide with the help of skilled trainers and an encouraging environment. Atlas School of English Language is a one stop solution for Learning English Language. Whatever your level, we have comprehensive courses to fit all your needs.  HOW ASEL IS DIFFERENT FROM OTHER ENGLISH LANGUAGE INSTITUTES:  ? Our Unique and Innovative approach is based on understanding concepts through various fun activities. ? Well trained and well qualified teachers from Lady Sri Ram College of Delhi University ? Regular tests with developmental reports.  ? Technology Aided classes to increase retention of the students via structured lessons taught through visual slides. ? Our classes provide basic clarity which is the stepping stone to real learning. ? We enable to increase the level of confidence and self esteem of our students. ? Our classes are highly flexible and can be chosen as per YOUR convenience. Also tailor made courses would be made in order to suit your needs and level. Timings are adjustable and can be re-scheduled. This ensures flexibility while maximising learning. ? Regular feedback is taken into consideration in order to match the needs of the enrolled candidates.  METHODOLOGY: ASEL has designed a unique teaching methodology which incorporates Audio Visual Aids and Specially Designed Interactive Sessions including various fun activities like: Role Play, Group Discussions, etc. Emphasis is laid on regular testing and direct communication through speaking. Perpetual improvisation is done in accordance with the feedback from the enrolled candidates in order to match the continually changing needs.  COURSES: ASEL offers specifically designed courses keeping in mind the different needs of the housewives, professionals and students. Details:
Amity Institute for Competitive Examinations is a name synonymous with unparalleled success. The track record of exemplary results that our students produce year after bears a testimony to this fact. Amity has always believed in recognizing and nurturing talents. In keeping with this tradition, Amity Institute of Competitive Examinations (AICE) has efficiently groomed and prepared numerous students, gearing them up to face the competitive exams so much so that they have left a trailblazing track record of success stories. In a span of just 10 years it has managed to carve a niche for itself in the competitive arena. Starting from Saket with 6 faculty members and 30 students in first year, AICE has since grown by leaps and bounds and today boasts of 6 centers including Vasundhara and Gurgaon.
The Amity Olympiad workshops, organized by Amity Institute for Competitive and Amity Centre for Science Olympiad are unique in every respect. The programme was designed specifically to help students master not only the fundamentals but also develop speed and accuracy in solving problems.
After the success of Olympiads, another programme Global Talent Search Exams (GTSE) was introduced in the year 2006 to recognize and award talented students who will be the torch bearers of Indias future.
We hope to continue with the good work in future and look forward to a long and fruitful association with you.Branch Details :-

Details:
NSB is actively involved since 1978 in training candidates seeking bank jobs from every nook and corner of India.With an experience of over 37 years, we have the singular distinction in India of helping thousands of young men and women to join Banks as Officers and Clerks. In Banks all over India, you see a situation in which every next Probationary Officer and Clerk during the past thirty-seven years has passed through the portals of NSB for his/her training.
National School of Banking is the only Institute in India specialising for years in Bank Recruitment Courses with a full-fledged Bank Examinations Research Department, headed by our Founder Chairman, late Shri E.K. Thakur. For years now, we have devoted ourselves mainly to BANK RECRUITMENT training for Officer and Clerical posts and year after year, thousands of our students have joined Banks as Probationary Officers and Clerks. Till today, over 87,000 students of NSB have joined Banks, Govt. Offices/Public Sector Organisations in Probationary Officer (P.O.) and Clerical cadres.

Name: Manya Education Pvt. Ltd.
Services Offered: PSAT Exam Coaching , SAT Coaching , GMAT Coaching ,
Details:
Manya Education (P) Ltd. (MEPL) was set up in 2002 as a first of its kind, one-stop solution provider in overseas education. Named after one of the 1008 avatars of Goddess Saraswati, Manya signifies the free flow of wisdom and consciousness while discriminating between wrong and right. In the last decade, MEPL has successfully established itself as the national leader in three broad domains namely:
- Study abroad test preparation
- Overseas admissions
- Skill building especially in language and communication training.MEPL is the Indian partner and the most successful International Division of The Princeton Review (TPR), the worlds leading test preparation service provider for tests such as the GMAT, GRE, SAT, IELTS and TOEFL. The Princeton Review was founded in 1981 and is headquartered in Framingham, MA. With a presence in 1000+ classroom locations over 17 countries, it has been a pioneer and leader, in helping students achieve their higher education goals for 30 years through college and graduate school test preparation and private tutoring. With more than 165 print and digital publications, the company provides students and their parents with the resources to research, apply to, prepare for, and learn how to pay for higher education. The Princeton Review partners with schools and guidance counselors throughout the US to assist in college readiness, test preparation and career planning services, helping more students pursue post-secondary education.

Name: Edstar
Services Offered: Big Data Analytics Online Training , R Analytics Online Training , GRE Coaching , SAT Coaching , GMAT Coaching ,
Details:
Edstar, set up in the year 2003 is a leading name in the field of Overseas Education. We operate through our network of 15 self-owned offices across India, and one in Kathmandu, Nepal. Each office is supported by well qualified professionals and education experts and works towards guiding Indian students in their admission requirements for overseas study.
Not only have we trained students in admission tests but have also helped over 2000 students set foot in a University of their choice across the world by means of our personalized coaching and counseling services through our locations across the country - major cities being Delhi, Bangalore, Mumbai, Kolkata, Pune etc. Backed by the expertise and strong industry connections of WLC College, our students have also found suitable placements with ease while still studying in foreign countries.
Be it Engineering, Medicine, Bio-technology, Law, Business Management, Fashion, Media, Art and Design or Hospitality to name a few, our end to end services have the best partners for studying in any destination overseas. Our major partners are spread mostly in UK, USA, New Zealand, Australia, Germany and Canada.
Thousands of satisfied and successful students bear testimony to the quality of our service and the missionary zeal of our consultants.
Not surprisingly, our students have landed in the most prestigious universities for the most sought after courses. This is further certified by the fact that the number of students availing our services is increasing with each passing day. Our reliability ensures flawless admission process and total satisfaction not only for the students but also for the partnering Universities.
